## 1. Tokens de Color

### Paleta Base

| Token Semántico | Clase Tailwind | Valor Hex | Uso |
|---|---|---|---|
| `color-bg` | `bg-bg` | `#070711` | Fondo principal / Canvas base |
| `color-surface` | `bg-surface` | `#0E0E1C` | Cards, modales, superficies elevadas |
| `color-surface-2` | `bg-surface-2` | `#16162A` | Inputs, nav, tooltips, items hover |
| `color-text` | `text-text` | `#F7EBEC` | Texto principal |
| `color-text-muted` | `text-muted` | `#9490A8` | Subtítulos, labels, placeholders |
| `color-text-disabled` | `text-disabled` | `#4A4860` | Estado desactivado |
| `color-border` | `border-border` | `#1F1F38` | Bordes de cards, inputs, divisores |
| `color-border-subtle` | `border-subtle` | `#141428` | Bordes de muy bajo contraste |

### Paleta de Acento

| Token | Clase Tailwind | Valor Hex | Uso |
|---|---|---|---|
| `color-primary` | `bg-primary` / `text-primary` | `#197BBD` | Acción principal, links, focus ring |
| `color-primary-hover` | `hover:bg-primary-hover` | `#1A8ED4` | Hover del acento principal |
| `color-primary-muted` | `bg-primary-muted` | `#197BBD1A` | Fondo sutil de badges, tags |
| `color-neon` | `bg-neon` / `text-neon` | `#39FF14` | Highlight disruptivo, decoración |
| `color-neon-muted` | `bg-neon-muted` | `#39FF141A` | Glow / Fondo tag neón |
| `color-danger` | `bg-danger` / `text-danger` | `#F71735` | Error, alerta, acción destructiva |
| `color-danger-muted` | `bg-danger-muted` | `#F717351A` | Fondo de mensajes de error |

### Reglas de Contraste (WCAG AA)

- Texto principal `#F7EBEC` sobre `#070711` → ratio ≈ 17:1 ✅
- Texto muted `#9490A8` sobre `#070711` → ratio ≈ 4.8:1 ✅
- Acento azul `#197BBD` sobre `#070711` → ratio ≈ 4.6:1 ✅ (mínimo para UI de gran tamaño)
- Neón `#39FF14` sobre `#070711` → ratio ≈ 12:1 ✅ — usar solo como highlight, no texto corrido

