## 10. Componentes Base — Especificaciones

### Botón

| Variante | Clases Tailwind | Uso |
|---|---|---|
| Primary (Solid) | `bg-primary text-text font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-primary-hover transition-colors duration-150 shadow-glow-primary` | CTA principal |
| Outline | `border border-primary text-primary font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors duration-150` | CTA secundario (ej. "Conectemos" en Navbar) |
| Ghost | `text-muted hover:text-text hover:bg-surface-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-md transition-colors duration-150` | Acciones terciarias |
| Danger | `bg-danger text-text font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:opacity-90 shadow-glow-danger` | Acciones destructivas |
| Neon Accent | `border border-neon text-neon font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-none hover:bg-neon/10 shadow-glow-neon transition-all duration-200` | Highlight disruptivo |

> **Tamaño mínimo táctil:** siempre ≥ 44px de altura → usar `min-h-[44px]`.

### Input

```
bg-surface-2 border border-border text-text placeholder:text-disabled
rounded px-4 py-3 text-base focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary/40
transition-shadow duration-150 w-full
```

### Card

```
bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6 shadow
hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-glow-subtle transition-all duration-200
```

