### Heading con Acento Neón

```html
<h2 class="font-heading font-black text-5xl lg:text-7xl text-text tracking-tight leading-none">
  IDEAS <span class="text-neon">TRANSFORMADAS</span>
</h2>
```

### Card Estándar

```html
<div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6
            hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-glow-subtle
            transition-all duration-200">
  <!-- contenido -->
</div>
```

### Botón Primario

```html
<button class="bg-primary text-text font-semibold text-sm px-6 py-3
               rounded-md min-h-[44px] hover:bg-primary-hover
               shadow-glow-primary transition-colors duration-150
               focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary/50">
  Escríbenos
</button>
```

### Botón Outline (Navbar CTA)

```html
<button class="border border-primary text-primary font-semibold text-sm
               px-5 py-2.5 rounded-none min-h-[44px]
               hover:bg-primary/10 hover:shadow-glow-primary
               transition-all duration-200 tracking-widest uppercase">
  CONECTEMOS
</button>
```
